@startuml UC_28_Handle_Global_Reports
title UC-28: Handle Global Reports

|User|
start
:(1) Open the global reports dashboard;
:(2) Filter or select a report;
:(3) Review the report details;
:(4) Delete one or more reports after handling;

|System|
:(5) Validate admin access;
:(6) Load reports using the selected filters;
:(7) Return the report details;
:(8) Delete the selected report records;
:(9) Return the updated report list;

stop
@enduml
